---
title: Cheesy Chicken Burger with Ballymaloe Relish with buttery herby potatoes
description: This chicken burger features a moreish Ballymaloe drizzle, scallion mayo and perhaps best of all, a golden chicken breast sandwiched between cheesy brioche buns. As if that's not enough, herby baby potatoes are the perfect thing to round out the dish.
